casebody.data:
Tuesday, June 1, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

97-1618. Ameritech Ohio v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 97-654-TP-CSS. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for leave to file a supplemental authority,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for leave to file a supplemental authority be, and hereby is, denied.

Resnick, J., not participating.
